== Bio 

- Postdoctoral Fellow (2022-present), [https://softmath.seas.harvard.edu/ Mahadevan Group], Applied Mathematics, Harvard University

- Postdoctoral Fellow (2022-2024), [https://portal.research.lu.se/en/organisations/lund-vision-group Vision Group], Biology, Lund University. 

- Postdoctoral Scholar (2020-2022), [http://www.fabiopas.it/index.html Pasqualetti Group], Mechanical Engineering, UC Riverside 

- Ph.D. (2019) in Mechanical and Aerospace Engineering, UC San Diego 

- B.Tech, M.Tech (2014) in Mechanical Engineering, IIT Madras

== Research
Optimization, Control, Statistical Physics, Machine Learning, Soft Matter

